Hello,

This email message is a notification to let you know that

  Uploaded by : cawiggins78 <cawiggins78@...> 
  Description : "EVP's: Techniques, Grading, History, and Classification" I got this off of the net. I AM NOT the author of this. I tried to email those responsible for permission to post this, but couldn't find the group or the author. If you know these folks, or are these folks, I will take the info down at your request. I find it relevant, helpful, and necessary information. Hopefully you will too. This may already be posted somewhere on the board that I am not aware of. Remember, I'm new to the group.

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/EVP-ITC/files/Chad%27s%20EVPs%20and%20Files/Relevant%20Files/EVP.pdf
